Uses of Package
aston.group17.model

  • Packages that use aston.group17.model 
    Package Description
    aston.group17.model  
  • Classes in aston.group17.model used by aston.group17.model 
    Class and Description
    Driver
    A Driver, who will join the Pump, Till and Shop and initally managed by the Station.
    Pump
    A Pump which contains a queue of Drivers, belongs to a Station instance and allows Driver to refill their Vehicle
    Shop
    A Shop which handles shopping Drivers, if they are going to shop, and sends Drivers to the Till when they are done shopping
    Vehicle
    A Vehicle belonging to a Driver, interacted with by the Driver, filling the tank of the Vehicle
